node.text:
Just a few of the items that I picked up the other day from Hearth & Hand’s new fall collection 🍂😍 Their fall stuff is my absolute fave!! I also spotted these metal picture frames that I had to have 🤩 they come in several different sizes! I’ve linked everything for y’all in my bio - just click on the link to shop ✨
.
.
#liketkit #LTKunder50 #LTKhome #LTKSeasonal @shop.ltk http://liketk.it/3lLxq

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by NIKOLE | TARGET BLOGGER on August 11, 2021 tagging @targetstyle, @target, and @talktargettomen. May be an image of 1 person, child and standing.

node.text: A day late but our big boy started 1st grade yesterday and had such a great time! 📚✏️ I can’t believe how grown up he looks!! 🥺 Has school started where you live? Let me know ⭐️

node.text: Name a cuter smiler than one that’s missing two front teeth 🙈😍 I’m honestly going to be so sad when Braylon’s front adult teeth come in. 😭 In other news, we switched out his old mattress for a new @simmonssleep memory foam mattress & he loves it SO much! Comfortable, affordable, & conveniently packaged in a box! Target is currently running a 10% off discount on Simmons Memory Foam Mattresses now through August 14th - check out my stories to see how easy it is to unbox & to shop! ⭐️ PS: it’s a little wrinkled since we JUST took it out of the box 🤪 #SimmonsPartner

node.text:
The NEW Hearth & Hand Fall collection is now available online & I am SO EXCITED 😍 It’s my favorite time of the year & I cannot wait to decorate! 🍁🍂 I’m doing a huge pickup order since a couple things that I wanted are already sold out online so make sure to check & see if in-store pickup is available for you! I’ve linked all of my faves for y’all - just click on the link in my bio to shop 💛
.
.
#liketkit #LTKstyletip #LTKunder50 #LTKhome @shop.ltk http://liketk.it/3lpPh
